836|"'It's not on earth, bless you,' replied the cook, happily; 'it's UNDERME--in the water. I got a bit warm setting there in the sun, and I justsays, \"I wish I was in a cold bath\"--just like that--and next minutehere I was! It's all part of the dream.'"|FALSE
