836|"'I don't know what you're talking about, and I wish you wouldn't muddleus with new names. Fire just happens. Nobody does it--not as a deed,you know,' Cyril explained. 'If they did the Phoenix wouldn't help them,because its a crime to set fire to things. Arsenic, or something theycall it, because it's as bad as poisoning people. The Phoenix wouldn'thelp THEM--father told me it wouldn't.'"|FALSE
