836|"'Now,' said Cyril, firmly, 'I know you'll be awfully surprised, andyou'll think it's not true and we are lunatics; but we aren't, and itis. Robert's got something inside his Norfolk--that's Robert, he's myyoung brother. Now don't be upset and have a fit or anything sir. Ofcourse, I know when you called your shop the \"Phoenix\" you never thoughtthere was one; but there is--and Robert's got it buttoned up against hischest!'"|FALSE
