836|"'If it's a dream,' said Robert, 'you will wake up directly, and thenyou'd be sorry if you'd sent us into a dream-asylum, because you mightnever get into the same dream again and let us out, and so we might staythere for ever, and then what about our sorrowing relatives who aren'tin the dreams at all?'"|FALSE
