836|"And then, just as the hopelessness and the helplessness were getting tobe almost more than they could bear, the two children suddenly felt thatextraordinary shrinking feeling that you always have when you are justgoing to vanish. And the next moment they had vanished, and the ReverendSeptimus was left alone with his aunts."|FALSE
