836|"     \"I love my little baby rabbit;     But oh! he has a dreadful habit     Of paddling out among the rocks     And soaking both his bunny socks.'"|FALSE
836|"'I don't think you'd care about the sons of the Phoenix, really,' saidRobert. 'I have heard that they don't do anything fiery. They only drinka great deal. Much more than other people, because they drink lemonadeand fizzy things, and the more you drink of those the more good youget.'"|FALSE
